--[[
    RHYTHM AUTOPLAY BOT - DYNAMIC RECEPTOR & KEYBIND ENGINE
    ----------------------------------------------------------------
    Features:
    - NEW: Truly Dynamic Key Mapping using direct Enum.KeyCode[KeyHint.ContentText] lookups.
    - NEW: Dynamic Receptor Scanner that parses "Receptor[num]" patterns (handles 1 to 100+ lanes).
    - NEW: On-screen Key Press and Hit History Log to diagnose missed notes/late releases.
    - NEW: Self-healing Receptor Key Cache to prevent frame-misses during layout updates.
    - Dual Tap vs Hold state engines (crisp 50ms taps vs sustained hold trails).
    - Auto-Scroll-Direction calibration (Upscroll & Downscroll layouts).
    - Multi-accuracy Modes (Perfect, Great, Good, Humanized Legit).
    - Draggable GUI Frame.
--]]

